_sText: Another insane map from BM The Baby Eatin Bishop of BW... in this one you fly though the air (on a much crazyer scale than "conveyor"), and smash panes of glass while in mid-air. then, go on a series of extreamly fast conveyor-belts, and launch in to the air and into a huge block of water.... loads more crazy stuff happens, then you drop a bomb... the end!
